{"data":[{"id":563767761,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"69de0d3ae019b068601b2ead73e63ecc","url_token":"ruo-huo-liu-xing","name":"若火流星","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/69de0d3ae019b068601b2ead73e63ecc","user_type":"people","headline":"小白","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":2,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563767761","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546274599,"updated_time":1546276218,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e直接指出错误，然后再说。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e看到再定义的时候其实还是有一点期待的，感觉是很奇特的思路，说不定就见证历史了！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然而...........我数学虽然不好，但是基于这是基于小学数学知识，我还是看懂了，至少个人认为这是错的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e舍去那一步错了。\u003c/b\u003e \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e ps:学过数学都知道，只能因为条件舍去，哪能因为结果舍去。否则大家随便循环论证各种命题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e详细：\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e解释一下-1属于质数的情况，其他两种情况一样。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2n属于B，其中很多数依赖于：-1属于质数\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后，舍去-1属于质数的情况时，其中那些依赖于 -1 属于质数的2n此时是否属于B就无法证明。整个证明随之失去意义。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后一提，\u003cb\u003e答主这种行为不支持\u003c/b\u003e，至于为什么，高票回答说的很清楚，我不认为这是什么怀疑精神，这是投机。但是基于还是高中生，\u003cb\u003e可以原谅。\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e答主解法链接：\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u00